abstract: The top free application in Apple’s App Store there for much of last week wasn’t a mobile game or a social network, but a tool of protest.

lead_paragraph: In a sign of the political mood in Taiwan, the top free application in Apple’s App Store there for much of last week wasn’t a mobile game or a social network, but a tool of protest.

headline.main: A Protest App Rises to the Top in Taiwan
headline.print_headline: Scandal in Taiwan Drives Downloads of Protest App
